    "ZHENG B leads with 36 publications, followed by LI J with 29, KARSSEMEIJER N with 27, and both MANN RM and WANG Y with 25.",
    "CHAN H-P and NISHIKAWA RM have 19 publications each, SECHOPOULOS I has 18, and MOY L and HOUSSAMI N each have 16.",
    "In terms of citation impact, KARSSEMEIJER N ranks highest with 2133 citations, while MANN RM and SECHOPOULOS I have 1499 and 1206 citations, respectively.",
    "The h-index indicates that KARSSEMEIJER N and ZHENG B are the most influential authors, with h-indices of 16 and 15, respectively.",
    "They are followed by LI J and MANN RM, each with an h-index of 13, and CHAN H-P, MOY L, SECHOPOULOS I, and WANG Y, each with an h-index of 11."
